---
---

<section id="blog" class="py-28 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-purple-400 font-medium text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Writing</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">From the Blog</h2>
      <div class="h-px w-16 bg-purple-700 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Thoughts on cloud infrastructure, open source, and building things in public.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured post -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <a
        href="https://tonedefdev.github.io/opendepot/blog/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group block bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-purple-700/50 rounded-xl p-8 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple-900/10"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-5">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium bg-purple-900/50 text-purple-400 border border-purple-700/40 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            OpenDepot
          </span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium bg-emerald-900/50 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-700/40 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            Open Source
          </span>
          <span class="text-zinc-600 text-xs ml-1">May 23, 2026</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors leading-snug">
          I got tired of paying JFrog for a secure OpenTofu / Terraform registry so I built my own
        </h3>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6">
          Self-hosted, Kubernetes-native, and GitOps-ready — this is the story of why I built OpenDepot and what
          it means for teams who want full control over their IaC supply chain without the enterprise price tag.
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-purple-400 group-hover:text-purple-300 font-medium text-sm transition-colors">
          Read on the OpenDepot blog
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <a
        href="https://tonedefdev.github.io/opendepot/blog/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-zinc-700 hover:border-purple-700/60 hover:bg-zinc-800/50 text-zinc-400 hover:text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-md text-sm font-semibold transition-colors"
      >
        View all posts
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
